# Native credential proxy (.claude/skills/use-native-credential-proxy)
# Opt out of the OneCLI gateway and supply Anthropic-compatible credentials from .env.
# When true, the credential below is injected into the container env directly.
# Used here to point the agent at a remote Ollama endpoint (Anthropic-compatible API).
# NANOCLAW_NATIVE_CREDENTIALS=true
# One of the following is required when the flag is true (for Ollama use a dummy):
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=ollama
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=
# Custom endpoint (Ollama tunnel / gateway):
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://your-ollama-tunnel.example.com
